* CREATED: 11/01/1999
* UPDATED: 06/04/2014
*
* MAINTENANCE RECORD:
*
* 7.2.2
*  PJS 06/04/2014
*   Updated ATGUIGETPROPS & ATGUISETPROPS for better compatibility with
*   2K2 version of these routines (null PROPS argument).
*
* 7.2.1
*  PJS 10/10/2013
*   Changed ATGUIVERSION constant from 1.4 to '1.4' to fix problems
*   when using D3 SET-NUM-FORMAT to set European number fomat.
*
* 7.1.2
*  PJS 12/17/2012
*   Fixed bad CASE syntax in ATGUIERROR (caused by 7.1.1 change).
*
* 7.1.1
*  PJS 08/22/2012
*   Updated ATGUIGETPROPS & ATGUISETPROPS to count PROPS instead of
*   CTLIDS (allows passing NULL for CTLIDS). Updated ATGUIERROR for
*   more flexible command parsing when formatting error message.
*  
* 7.0.4
*  PJS 08/09/2010
*   Updated ATGUIINIT2 & ATGUIERROR to show version numbers in GRINVVER
*   error message.
*
* 7.0.3
*  PJS 03/25/2010
*   Added definitions for new grid FocusStyle & PasteMode properties.
*
* 7.0.2
*  PJS 11/15/2009
*   Moved error messages & other text out of ATGUIEQUATES and into
*   ATGUIERRMSG to eliminate code lines longer than 999 (helps make
*   upgrading simpler since FTCHK does not get compiled automatically
*   before performing the upgrade).
*
* 7.0.1
*  PJS 10/08/2009
*   Updated for GUI version 1.4
*
* 5.3.5
*  PJS 01/23/2008
*   Changed 'Template' to 'Project' in error message GRINVVER (5005).
*
* 5.3.4
*  PJS 08/01/2006
*   Added definition of GXROOT object.
*
* 5.3.3
*  PJS 07/24/2006
*   Added OI (OpenInsight CTO) platform support.
*
* 5.3.2
*  PJS 07/03/2006
*   Add equate for new &PRINTER and &SCREEN objects, and equates for
*   printer properties.
*
* 5.3.1
*  PJS 05/05/2006
*   Updated GUI version to 1.3. Added new GESTATUS event, GPSTATE,
*   GPCOLSIZABLE, GPCOLHINT, GPALTCOLOR properties. Added GCFONTDIALOG
*   and GCCOLORDIALOG command constants.
*
* 5.1.3
*  PJS 12/09/2005
*   Added definition for GPCUSTOM property
*
* 5.1.2
*  PJS 10/27/2004
*   Update for GUI version 1.2. Added GPMAXLEN, GPMAXLINES, GPMAXDROP,
*   GPREQUIRED, GPFIXEDCOLS, GPICON, GPSELSTART, GPSELLENGTH, GPHELPTYPE
*   property codes. Added GEDEACTIVATECELL, GEACTIVATEROW, GEDEACTIVATEROW
*   GEHELP event codes. Added GMHELP method code. Added new key constants.
*
* 4.0.5
*  PJS 08/06/2002
*   Added new property code: GPEXTENSION for use by 4GL products to
*   save and restore private data
*
* 4.0.4
*  PJS 09/26/2001
*   Removed Timer control, event and method (only available in beta
*   version, not supported in production version since ATGUICHECKEVENT
*   can be used instead)
*
* 4.0.3
*  PJS 09/19/2001
*   Changed version number from 1.0 to 1.1 due to added functionality
*
* 4.0.2
*  PJS 05/24/2001
*   Added new properties, controls and events for updated GUI engine
*
* 4.0.1
*  PJS 09/25/2000
*   CLEANUP FOR ACCUTERM 2000 RELEASE
*
**************************************************************************
